dct_description_sm: Map shows populates areas, notable buildings, churches, schools, roads, railways, bridges, powerlines, walls and fences, landmarks, mines and quarries, vegetation, and water features. Relief shown by contours with a 20 meter interval and spot heights. Includes location map, index to streets, glossary, and guide to numbered features. "This map is red-light readable." "Map information as of 1993." "WGS 84." "Grid--1,000 meter UTM zone 34." "Printed by NIMA." "This sheet falls within NL 34-07, 1501, 1:250,000 and 2985 I & II, 3085 III & IV, M709, 1:50,000." "NSN 7643014339852"
